<typeStatus id="54C2479FFF81C508FF12F854FF57F9E0" box="[196,255,1546,1572]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Type</typeStatus>
.
</emphasis>
In Chevrolat’s collection at 
<collectionCode id="ED6861F8FF81C508FD8EF854FD18F9E0" box="[600,688,1546,1572]" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/8z6v-f8is" name="Saskatchewan Museum of Natural History" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">SMNH</collectionCode>
, under the name “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C7982BEFF81C508FC51F855FAE4F9E0" authority="Chv., Rev. Zool. 1866" authorityName="Chv., Rev. Zool." authorityYear="1866" box="[903,1356,1546,1572]" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Lixus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hypocrita">
<emphasis id="B90D252FFF81C508FC51F855FB97F9E0" box="[903,1087,1547,1572]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Lixus hypocrita</emphasis>
Chv., Rev. Zool. 
<number id="3DB1EB1AFF81C508FAD9F854FAE4F9E0" box="[1295,1356,1546,1572]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" value="1866.0">1866</number>
</taxonomicName>
, p. 
<number id="3DB1EB1AFF81C508FAA1F854FA3FF9E0" box="[1399,1431,1546,1572]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" value="27.0">27</number>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F36EB9ADFF81C508FF41F86EFEAAF98E" box="[151,258,1584,1610]" name="Spain" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Hispania</collectingCountry>
, Aranjues, D. Lethierry, 
<emphasis id="B90D252FFF81C508FDF5F86EFDC1F98D" box="[547,617,1584,1609]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">ferula</emphasis>
” is a female pinned through the right elytron (elytra hardly separated, fore right leg missing), bearing the handwritten label: “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C7982BEFF81C508FCF4F80BFBB0F9AB" authority="Chv." authorityName="Chv." box="[802,1048,1621,1647]" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Lixus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hypocrita">
<emphasis id="B90D252FFF81C508FCF4F80BFC71F9AA" box="[802,985,1621,1646]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Lixus hypocrita</emphasis>
Chv.
</taxonomicName>
aranjeus, ombellifera a fl. jaune, Lett. sp.”, and fitting the description with 
<typeStatus id="54C2479FFF81C508FD43F824FD61F950" box="[661,713,1658,1684]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">type</typeStatus>
locality as Aranjuez. It is here designated as 
<typeStatus id="54C2479FFF81C508FB26F824FAF6F950" box="[1264,1374,1658,1684]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">lectotype</typeStatus>
with “ 
<typeStatus id="54C2479FFF81C508FF77F8FEFE81F97E" box="[161,297,1696,1722]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Lectotypus</typeStatus>
, Ƥ, 
<taxonomicName id="4C7982BEFF81C508FE8FF8FEFD79F97E" authority="Chev., Gultekin" authorityName="Chev., Gultekin" box="[345,721,1696,1722]" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Lixus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hypocrita">
<emphasis id="B90D252FFF81C508FE8FF8FEFDB8F97D" box="[345,528,1696,1721]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Lixus hypocrita</emphasis>
Chev., Gültekin
</taxonomicName>
des. 
<number id="3DB1EB1AFF81C508FCDBF8FEFCE6F97E" box="[781,846,1696,1722]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" value="2006.0">2006</number>
”.
</paragraph>
